casebody.data:
Clarence Alfred BREWER, a Minor, by L. D. Brewer, His Next Friend, v. ST. LOUIS-SAN FRANCISCO RAILWAY COMPANY, a Corporation. No. 559. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. April 11, 1932. F. A. Rittenhouse, of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellant. E. T. Miller, of St. Louis, Mo., for appel-lee.

Before LEWIS and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges, and POLLOCK, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, for failure to prosecute.
